    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK302">
<l>cellā viṭattuc ciṉantītu celliṭattu</l>
<l>millataṉiṟ tīya piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Anger is bad, even when it cannot injure; when it can injure; there is no greater evil.</l>
